{"tid":1862644,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] PES MOBILE 2020 討論帖 (166) 食屎啦牛佬","createTime":"2020-02-04T17:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T07:58:40.000Z","uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8b5f811479dbe13b393953edf108bd2760fd84","tid":1862644,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPToUF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPToUF5.jpg&h=ebe22e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n● 官網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.konami.com%2Fwepes%2Fmobile%2Fen%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=5b8c06a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/</a><br />\n● Download Link<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fpes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer%2Fid1117270703%3Fmt%3D8&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=81a8d3a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.konami.pesam&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=c38ac6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam</a><br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量雙金/一黑起手，抽中既球員可以睇下下面既推薦List，如果無亦可以問下各位巴打，當然唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=48282f58\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=59baeacd\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n●畫面調整<br />\n新手入game 第一件事畫質轉60fps<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38hp4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38hp4m.jpg&h=66c1328d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但30fps low quality 比較慳電<br />\n<br />\n教練，球員，沒有最強只有更強<br />\n因該每次更新，Konami 都會暗改教練球員走位，唔會通知，要靠老手用過先知<br />\n<br />\n●實時系統<br />\n每周四維護6小時（10am-4pm)後，會按照現實球員表現而調整球員狀態；<br />\n另有巴打（牛佬）隨時更新球員實際操作表現（暗改），詳情要留意留言<br />\n<br />\n●教練更新<br />\n即日起，可簽入不同版本的同名教練。每日更新3次，已擁有的教練不能再簽下<br />\n<br />\n●拍賣<br />\n根本球員條件（國籍，球會，年歲，能力）買球探組合球員<br />\n詳情：PES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=59baeacd\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mk94DHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmk94DHT.jpg&h=b5e7e1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRu8kWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRu8kWe.jpg&h=6f5e2c67&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"908b494bc801e7b39d4364a088c3f339461baf74","tid":1862644,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:39:39.000Z","msg":"屌 (156)至啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328c7982c821a11cec01b43b43144433390d7390","tid":186264